avdta.network.node

Class IntersectionControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.network.node.IntersectionControl
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Diverge, Highway, Merge, StopSign, TBR, TrafficSignal

    public abstract class IntersectionControl
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an abstract class to implement intersection controls (Stops, Conflict Regions, Signals, etc.). Intersection Control is implemented separately from a node so that each node can have a different intersection control.
    node Indicates on which Node this intersection control is present.
    See Also:
    Merge, Diverge, TrafficSignal, TBR
